== 關於電影 ==
《聖獄：耶路撒冷》是一部殭屍/附體恐怖片，<ref name=WGTC>{{cite web |url=http://wegotthiscovered.com/movies/jeruzalem-review/ |title=JeruZalem Review. |work=Wegotthiscovered.com |author=Matt Donato |date=January 2016 |accessdate=25 April 2016}}</ref>影片原名中的大寫字母{{lang|en|Z}}代表{{lang|en|Zombie}}（殭屍）。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://festivalreviews.org/2016/01/30/movie-review-jeruzalem-2016-israeli-zombie-film |title=Movie Review: JERUZALEM (2016) Israeli Zombie Film! |work=Festivalreviews.org |author=Gilbert Seah |date=30 January 2016 |accessdate=25 April 2016}}</ref>多倫·帕茲和約雅夫·帕茲撰寫了本片的劇本兼導演，{{tsl|en|Yael Grobglas|耶兒·葛洛格拉斯}}、[[揚·圖馬肯|揚·圖馬肯]]、{{tsl|en|Danielle Jadelyn|丹妮兒·潔德琳}}和湯姆·格拉齊亞尼主演，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.thehollywoodnews.com/2015/08/30/jeruzalem-review-090451 |title=Jeruzalem review. FrightFest 2015: “A tense and often scary film” |work=Thehollywoodnews.com |date=30 August 2015 |author=Luke Ryan Baldock |accessdate=25 April 2016}}</ref>電影於2015年7月10日的{{tsl|en|Jerusalem Film Festival|耶路撒冷影展}}上首映，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://variety.com/2015/film/news/jerusalem-film-festival-amy-jeruzalem-1201537995 |title=Jerusalem Film Festival Opens With ‘Amy,’ ‘Jeruzalem’ and ‘Tikkun’ |work=Variety.com |date=10 July 2015 |author=Debra Kamin |accessdate=25 April 2016}}</ref>之後也推出了{{lang|en|DVD}}和{{lang|en|Blu-ray}}。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://iris.theaureview.com/dvd-review-jeruzalem-israel-2015 |title=DVD Review: Jeruzalem (Israel, 2015). |work=Iris.theaureview.com |author=Ryan Champion |date=4 February 2016 |accessdate=25 April 2016 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161012222633/http://iris.theaureview.com/dvd-review-jeruzalem-israel-2015/ |archive-date=2016-10-12 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>《聖》片在[[耶路撒冷|耶路撒冷]]取景攝製，包括耶城的數處古蹟、古建築和宗教景點，同時也給出了這些景點的背景訊息。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://redcarpetcrash.com/movie-review-jeruzalem-makes-good-use-of-google-glass |title=Movie Review: ‘JeruZalem’ Makes Good Use Of Google Glass |work=Redcarpetcrash.com |date=16 January 2016 |author=Bradley Smith |accessdate=25 April 2016}}</ref>影片靈感源自《[[塔木德|塔木德]]》中的一句對《[[耶利米書|耶利米書]]》的註解（解經集）：「人間有三個地獄之門—荒漠，深海，以及耶路撒冷。」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sacred-texts.com/jud/t02/eru06.htm|title=p. 43 - R. Jeremiah ben Elazar said again. "Hell has three gates: One in the desert, one in the sea, and one in Jerusalem."}}</ref>多倫·帕茲和約雅夫·帕茲也是本片的製片人，他們自己籌集了{{USD|160,000}}的預算。目前電影已經售至世界各地，包括委內瑞拉、美國、英國、德國、法國、荷蘭、比利時、盧森堡、印度、菲律賓以及日本等。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.timesofisrael.com/its-the-talmud-with-zombies-in-new-israeli-horror-film/ |title=It’s the Talmud — with zombies! — in new Israeli horror film. |work=Timesofisrael.com |date=28 August 2015 |author=Lauri Donahue |accessdate=25 April 2016}}</ref>

